Mixin 的列子：

```dart
class A {
   void printMsg() => print('A'); 
}
mixin B {
    void printMsg() => print('B'); 
}
mixin C {
    void printMsg() => print('C'); 
}

class BC extends A with B, C {}
class CB extends A with C, B {}

main() {
    var bc = BC();
    bc.printMsg();

    var cb = CB();
    cb.printMsg();
}
```

输出结果：

```dart
C
B

Process finished with exit code 0
```

